# Tailwind CSS Rules

## Class Organization

Order classes logically:
1. Layout (flex, grid, position)
2. Sizing (w, h, p, m)
3. Typography (text, font)
4. Colors (bg, text color, border)
5. Effects (shadow, opacity, blur)
6. Transitions/Animations

```tsx
// ✅ Organized
<div className="flex items-center justify-between w-full p-4 text-sm text-white bg-gray-900 rounded-lg shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">

// ❌ Random order
<div className="shadow-lg text-sm flex bg-gray-900 p-4 rounded-lg text-white items-center w-full">
```

## Custom Animations

### Tailwind Config
```js
// tailwind.config.js
module.exports = {
  theme: {
    extend: {
      animation: {
        'pulse-bpm': 'pulse var(--pulse-duration, 1s) ease-in-out infinite',
        'glow': 'glow 2s ease-in-out infinite',
        'orbit': 'orbit var(--orbit-duration, 10s) linear infinite',
        'float': 'float 3s ease-in-out infinite',
      },
      keyframes: {
        pulse: {
          '0%, 100%': { transform: 'scale(1)', opacity: '1' },
          '50%': { transform: 'scale(1.05)', opacity: '0.8' },
        },
        glow: {
          '0%, 100%': { filter: 'drop-shadow(0 0 10px var(--glow-color, #22c55e))' },
          '50%': { filter: 'drop-shadow(0 0 30px var(--glow-color, #22c55e))' },
        },
        orbit: {
          '0%': { transform: 'rotate(0deg) translateX(var(--orbit-radius, 100px)) rotate(0deg)' },
          '100%': { transform: 'rotate(360deg) translateX(var(--orbit-radius, 100px)) rotate(-360deg)' },
        },
        float: {
          '0%, 100%': { transform: 'translateY(0)' },
          '50%': { transform: 'translateY(-10px)' },
        },
      },
    },
  },
};
```

### CSS Custom Properties for Dynamic Values
```css
/* src/app/globals.css */
:root {
  --pulse-duration: 1s;
  --glow-color: #22c55e;
  --orbit-radius: 100px;
  --orbit-duration: 10s;
}
```

### Setting CSS Variables from React
```tsx
'use client';

import { useEffect } from 'react';

export function useBPM(tempo: number) {
  useEffect(() => {
    const pulseDuration = 60 / tempo; // seconds per beat
    document.documentElement.style.setProperty(
      '--pulse-duration',
      `${pulseDuration}s`
    );
  }, [tempo]);
}
```

## Color Classes

### Spotify Green Theme
```tsx
// Primary green
className="bg-[#1DB954] text-black"

// With Tailwind colors
className="bg-green-500 hover:bg-green-600"

// Custom in config
// tailwind.config.js
colors: {
  spotify: {
    green: '#1DB954',
    black: '#191414',
  }
}
// Usage
className="bg-spotify-green text-spotify-black"
```

### Dark Mode
```tsx
// Automatic dark mode support
className="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 text-gray-900 dark:text-white"

// In tailwind.config.js
module.exports = {
  darkMode: 'class', // or 'media'
}
```

## Responsive Design

### Mobile-First
```tsx
// Base = mobile, then add larger breakpoints
<div className="p-4 md:p-6 lg:p-8">
<div className="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
<div className="text-sm md:text-base lg:text-lg">
```

### Container
```tsx
<div className="container mx-auto px-4">
```

## Common Patterns

### Centered Content
```tsx
// Flex center
<div className="flex items-center justify-center min-h-screen">

// Grid center
<div className="grid place-items-center min-h-screen">
```

### Card
```tsx
<div className="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl shadow-lg p-6">
```

### Button
```tsx
<button className="px-4 py-2 bg-green-500 hover:bg-green-600 text-white font-medium rounded-lg transition-colors">
```

### Glass Effect
```tsx
<div className="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-lg border border-white/20 rounded-xl">
```

## Animation Utilities

### Transitions
```tsx
// All properties
className="transition-all duration-300"

// Specific properties
className="transition-colors duration-200"
className="transition-transform duration-500"
className="transition-opacity duration-150"
```

### Timing Functions
```tsx
className="ease-linear"
className="ease-in"
className="ease-out"
className="ease-in-out"
```

### Reduced Motion
```tsx
// Respect user preference
className="animate-pulse motion-reduce:animate-none"
className="transition-transform motion-reduce:transition-none"
```

## SVG Styling

```tsx
// Fill and stroke
<circle className="fill-green-500 stroke-white stroke-2" />

// Hover states
<circle className="fill-green-500 hover:fill-green-400 transition-colors" />

// Drop shadow for glow
<circle className="drop-shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(34,197,94,0.5)]" />
```

## Avoid These Patterns

❌ Inline styles when Tailwind class exists
```tsx
// Bad
<div style={{ marginTop: '16px' }}>
// Good
<div className="mt-4">
```

❌ `@apply` for one-off styles
```css
/* Bad - just use the class */
.my-button {
  @apply px-4 py-2 bg-blue-500;
}
```

❌ Too many arbitrary values
```tsx
// Bad - add to config instead
<div className="w-[347px] h-[892px] bg-[#1a2b3c]">

// Good - use config or standard values
<div className="w-80 h-full bg-gray-800">
```

❌ Conflicting classes
```tsx
// Bad
<div className="flex block hidden">
```
